  <Entries>
    <Entry>
      <ID>1</ID>
      <DefaultText>You pluck Vareth from your bag, and nearly drop it. The edges of it *feel* sharp - but thankfully, not sharp enough to cut. 
{SCRIPT: Node displays if player has ITM_RINGA_ShadowRingVareth}
</DefaultText>
      <FemaleText />
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <ID>2</ID>
      <DefaultText>You pull both rings from your bags and hold them in opposing palms. Even at this distance, the force repelling them from each other is extraordinary. </DefaultText>
      <FemaleText />
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <ID>3</ID>
      <DefaultText>With a grunt, you pull Areph from your bag. It feels monstrously heavy for such a small, plain thing.  
{SCRIPT: Node displays if player has ITM_RINGA_ShadowRingAreph}</DefaultText>
      <FemaleText />
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <ID>4</ID>
      <DefaultText>You retrieve the ring from your bags again. 
{SCRIPT: Player has one of the rings but not both.} </DefaultText>
      <FemaleText />
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <ID>5</ID>
      <DefaultText>""
{GAVIN: Not for Beta. Marked as Should Not Play for now.}</DefaultText>
